title: 152. Andy & DJ Cruise The Internet
itunes:title: 152. Andy & DJ Cruise The Internet
description: Andy & DJ went on a cruise! On today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss the latest stories happening across the internet. They start with Jon Gruden's emails that led to his termination, followed by the Loudoun Country School District's transgender sexual assault case and what the supply chain crisis means for America's future.
